comments: Carter Jr. (ORL) maintains a legal guarding position on Jokic (DEN) in the post.
Bamba (ORL) legally contests Gordon's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
Harris (ORL) remains in bounds and does not step out of bounds before he releases the pass.
Wagner (ORL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Jokic (DEN) moves his pivot foot.  The traveling violation occurs before any possible foul.
Jokic (DEN) legally contests Carter Jr.'s (ORL) driving shot attempt and the contact is incidental as Carter Jr. returns to the floor.

Harris (ORL) places a hand on Barton (DEN) but does not apply force and the contact is marginal as Barton drifts to the side during his jump shot attempt.  The contact to the hand after Barton's release is incidental.

Gordon (DEN) commits a take foul on Anthony (ORL).  The game clock expires and after communicating with the Replay Center, it is determined that the foul occurs before the expiration of the game clock with 2.3 seconds remaining.
